msgstr "從最高頻率開始繪製點。"

#: data/effects/audiospectrum.xml:46
#, kde-format
msgid "Line Tension"
msgstr "線條張力"

#: data/effects/audiospectrum.xml:47
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Affects the amount of curve in the line interpolating between points. 0.0 = "
"a straight line between points. 100 = very curved lines between points. "
"Values < 0 and > 100 will cause loops in the lines. Only applies to line "
"graph type."
msgstr ""
"影響點與點之間內插補點曲線的曲度。0.0 代表點之間為直線，100 代表點之間的線的"
"曲度非常大。小於 0 或大於 100 的數值會造成線段繞圈。只適用於線條圖類型。"

#: data/effects/audiospectrum.xml:50
#, kde-format
msgid "Points"
msgstr "點數"

#: data/effects/audiospectrum.xml:51
#, kde-format
